name: Burning Field
description:
This is the annual event after harvest, the farmer will burn the field for getting moister and easy to cultivate.

this picture is taken in Ranca Buaya Beach in West Java, Indonesia.

it is really rare to have a rice field face to face with the ocean, Indian Ocean.

This Picture is taken with my Nikon FM2 and using Rollei Black and White Film. my first picnic with my adventurous friend in the Pandemic.
